---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import {Image} from 'astro:assets';
import avatarImage from '../assets/avatar.png';
---

<Layout
        title="About Luke | Full-Stack Developer with 10 Years Experience"
        description="Meet Luke, a seasoned full-stack developer with a decade of experience. Specializing in robust web applications, from backend architecture to frontend design."
>
    <div class="bg-yellow-100 py-8 border-y-4 border-black min-h-[calc(100vh-288px)]">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] relative">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-400 border-4 border-black transform rotate-12 translate-x-8 -translate-y-8"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-pink-400 border-4 border-black rounded-full -translate-x-10 translate-y-10"></div>

                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black transform -rotate-1 break-words mb-8 relative z-10">
                    About Luke</h1>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 relative z-10">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
                        <div class="w-full md:w-48 bg-orange-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1 relative">
                            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-400 border-4 border-black transform rotate-12 translate-x-2 -translate-y-2"></div>
                            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden border-4 border-black mb-2">
                                <Image
                                    src={avatarImage}
                                    alt="Luke - Full Stack Developer"
                                    class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                                />
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-center font-bold text-sm">@logical-luke</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 bg-blue-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform -rotate-1">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Journey</h2>
                            <p>My journey in tech began with curiosity about how things work. I tackle complex
                                problems with enthusiasm, turning them into efficient applications. Through the years,
                                I've developed a deep understanding of software architecture and best practices. My
                                passion for learning drives me to stay current with emerging technologies and industry trends.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
                        <div class="flex-1 bg-green-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1 relative">
                            <div class="absolute -bottom-3 left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-400 border-4 border-black transform -rotate-12 -translate-x-2 translate-y-2"></div>
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Developer</h2>
                            <p>As a full-stack developer with 10 years of experience, I've mastered both frontend design
                            and backend architecture. My expertise lies in crafting robust web applications that solve
                            real-world problems. I take pride in writing clean, maintainable code that stands the test of time.
                            Each project is an opportunity to deliver solutions that exceed expectations.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 bg-yellow-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform -rotate-1">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Approach</h2>
                            <p>I believe in creating scalable, user-friendly solutions that drive business growth.
                            My approach combines technical expertise with practical business understanding. Every line
                            of code is written with performance and maintainability in mind. I focus on delivering
                            seamless end-to-end applications that users love to interact with.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-purple-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Person</h2>
                        <p>I'm a proud husband and father, finding joy in the simple moments with my family. Our home
                        is made complete by our cat and dog, who add their own charm to our daily adventures. We love
                        exploring beautiful landscapes together, making memories in nature. Whether it's a weekend hike
                        or a family game night, these moments keep me grounded and inspired. I bring this same sense
                        of dedication and joy to my professional work.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-pink-200 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform -rotate-1 relative">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-400 border-4 border-black rounded-full translate-x-2 -translate-y-2"></div>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Geek</h2>
                        <p>Outside of coding, I'm an avid gamer who enjoys both classic titles and new releases.
                        My bass guitar offers a creative outlet, and I enjoy jamming to various genres in my spare time.
                        Board game nights are a regular occurrence in our household, where strategy and fun combine.
                        These hobbies help maintain a healthy work-life balance and often inspire creative
                        problem-solving approaches in my development work.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>


